column2: Top names for baby girls in England and Wales, 2010
These rankings have been produced using the exact spelling of the name given at birth registration. Similar names
with different spellings have been counted separately. Births where the name was not stated have been
excluded from these figures. Of the 352,199 baby girls in the 2010 dataset, 6 were excluded for this reason.
